Henry Meja hit the winner for the Brewers in the 81st minute to complete the comeback after JacksoN Macharia had restored parity for the league leaders. Tusker on Tuesday went seven points clear at the top of the Football Kenya Federation Premier League (FKF-PL), following their hard fought 2-1 win over Nzoia Sugar at Moi International Sports Centre, Kasarani in Nairobi. 

Teen sensation Henry Meja hit the winner for the Brewers in the 81st minute to complete the comeback after Faraj Odeny had restored parity for the league leaders after Hillary Simiyu had given the visitors a 47th minute lead. 



